#-    Hi, Draziwrok!

If you are reading this, you will notice that the chest contains items that I owe you. However, since this is a minor crime, I tried to give you more than what I originally owed you. If you ever need anything, feel free to contact me at
#- any time! I truly regret that I killed your horse, please accept my apology!

